CLAUDE.md
# docker-compose bind-mounted controller state (./data) + optional caddy dirs
/data/
/caddy-data/
/caddy-config/
.dev-backend.log
.dev-backend.pid
.dev-frontend.log
.dev-frontend.pid
# private key material must never be committed (bundle signing key, TLS, etc.)
*.pem
*.key
*.cred
# Exception: the localcompile contract corpus ships ONE throwaway test-only Ed25519 signing
# key (NOT any production key) so the signing-on golden fixture can byte-freeze the
# bundle.sig / signing-pubkey.pem path. It is generated under testdata and bound only to the
# test signer; see docs/spec/compiler/io-contract.md (the golden corpus).
!internal/localcompile/testdata/contract/signing/test-signing-key.pem